column5: Went out with my 6 year old today.  Used Terry Goy thanks to the recommendations of the members here....good operation.  Slow day, but we managed 45 in total and 14 keepers.  Great time spent with my dude and he is asking when we can go again!
Great day! To a six year old, 45 fish seems like a million. How was the snow/slush layer?
Slush was brutal...but the warmer temps made it doable
Nice to hear.  Great to see kids get out and enjoy this tradition.
